        {
            "title": "摩根士丹利押注英鎊將在2026年觸及脫歐公投以來高點",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xpPZIn6aFXjChDCAd_.pDw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/63c89a83b5abfe84b297957ce10a2504\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:摩根士丹利;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/摩根士丹利\">摩根士丹利</a>押注，在英國11月公佈預算後英鎊將上漲，在明年觸及十年高點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根士丹利建議投資者在英國財政大臣蕾切爾·里夫斯11月26日公佈財政計畫前，趁英鎊回調時建立多頭頭寸。該行預計到2026年中英鎊將從當前低於1.35美元的水平攀升至1.45美元，上一次達到該水平還是在2016年英國脫歐公投前。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根士丹利G-10貨幣策略主管David Adams在該行Cause and FX播客中表示，「在預算擔憂、換倉與套利交易，以及美元走弱這一論調之間，我們很樂意在別人因預算而拋售英鎊時買入。」</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-8c1b04a2-90a1-34a4-afc0-6a91192ecf59-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今年英鎊兌美元匯率已上漲逾7%，但自7月初觸及四年高點後漲勢已趨緩。這既因美元匯率趨穩，也源於投資者對英國財政困境的擔憂。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/qxtoV5kOi01v1boUy4fyBw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/de6b2fb63c23cb2f8693ee8ec693b0cd\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Adams的立場反映了他對英鎊長期看漲的觀點，而越來越多的銀行預計英鎊將在預算案公佈前走弱。根據彭博外匯調查，多數策略師認為到明年中期英鎊至多溫和漲至1.38美元水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Morgan Stanley Bets on Post-Brexit Pound High in 2026 (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%91%A9%E6%A0%B9%E5%A3%AB%E4%B8%B9%E5%88%A9%E6%8A%BC%E6%B3%A8%E8%8B%B1%E9%8E%8A%E5%B0%87%E5%9C%A82026%E5%B9%B4%E8%A7%B8%E5%8F%8A%E8%84%AB%E6%AD%90%E5%85%AC%E6%8A%95%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E9%AB%98%E9%BB%9E-153201688.html",
